metadata.name: NINKI Mother of Mankind
metadata.description:
"NINKI Mother of Mankind" by Stalomir (2022)

She came to New World with ENKI and MELKI.

MELKI - the messanger of lord, said: "To spread our will on New World, there is need to continue research on New Man."

With code of two entities, ADAPA, sibling of MARDUK, has born. 

Message to ANSHAR has been sended.
